Package: mwmap
Title: Create Maps of Malawi Administrative Boundaries
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chifundo", "Bita", , "bitac.analytics@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for creating publication-ready maps of Malawi at
    multiple administrative levels (country, region, district, and traditional
    authority). Includes spatial boundary data, choropleth mapping, district
    highlighting, point plotting, and a collection of Malawi-themed colour
    palettes suitable for health, agriculture, and socioeconomic visualizations.
